    {
      "name": "📖 API Reference",
      "description": "# Admin API Reference\n\nBase URL: `{{base_url}}` (default `http://localhost:8080/api/v1`) · 47 routes.\n\nThis folder is documentation only — no requests to run. Every route below is a working request somewhere else in this collection; use this as the map. A fuller version with sample bodies for every endpoint is also published at the artifact link the team shares separately.\n\n## Authentication\n\n| Header | Checked by | Required on | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `X-API-Key` | TenantMiddleware | everything except `/platform/*` | Identifies the tenant. Format `sk_live_<64 hex>`, shown once at tenant creation / rotate-key, stored server-side as a SHA-256 hash. |\n| `Authorization: Bearer <token>` | AuthMiddleware | `/admin/*` (role `admin`) and `/platform/*` (role `superadmin`) | Carries `user_id`, `role`, `tenant_id` (empty for superadmin). A `superadmin` token is rejected outright if its `tenant_id` is non-empty, on every route — a tenant-scoped token can never be treated as platform-level. An admin token is rejected if its `tenant_id` doesn't match the tenant resolved from `X-API-Key`. Admin/staff tokens come from `POST /login`; superadmin tokens come from `POST /platform/login`. |\n\n## Response format\n\n**Single resource**\n```json\n{ \"success\": true, \"data\": { \"...\": \"resource\" } }\n```\n\n**List**\n```json\n{ \"success\": true, \"data\": [ \"...\" ], \"meta\": { \"total\": 42, \"page\": 1, \"limit\": 20 } }\n```\n\n**Error**\n```json\n{ \"success\": false, \"message\": \"destination not found\" }\n```\n\n## Platform · Login & Admin Users\n_Not tenant-scoped. The first platform user is bootstrapped at server startup from `SUPERADMIN_EMAIL` / `SUPERADMIN_PASSWORD` (see `.env.example`) — it never overwrites an existing account._\n\n| Method | Path | Auth | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/platform/login` | public | `{ email, password }` → `{ token }` (role `superadmin`) |\n| POST | `/platform/admins` | superadmin | Add another platform user. Omit `password` to auto-generate one (returned once). |\n| GET | `/platform/admins` | superadmin | `?page&limit` |\n| PUT | `/platform/admins/:id/status` | superadmin | `{ status: active \\| suspended }`. Refuses to suspend the last active user. |\n\n## Platform · Tenants\n_Not tenant-scoped._\n\n| Method | Path | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/platform/tenants` | Creates a tenant, returns `api_key` once. If `contact_email` is set, also bootstraps a first `admin` tenant-user login and returns `login.password` once. |\n| GET | `/platform/tenants` | `?page&limit` |\n| GET | `/platform/tenants/:id` | |\n| PUT | `/platform/tenants/:id/status` | `{ status: active \\| suspended }` |\n| POST | `/platform/tenants/:id/rotate-key` | Invalidates the old key immediately. |\n\n## Platform · Tenant Subscriptions\n_Not tenant-scoped. Internal plan/status tracking only — no live payment provider wired in yet._\n\n| Method | Path | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/platform/tenants/:id/subscription` | `{ plan }` — `free \\| basic \\| pro \\| enterprise`, defaults to `free`. 409 if the tenant already has one. |\n| GET | `/platform/tenants/:id/subscription` | |\n| PUT | `/platform/tenants/:id/subscription/plan` | `{ plan }` — starts a fresh 30-day period. |\n| POST | `/platform/tenants/:id/subscription/cancel` | Sets status to `canceled`; plan/period left intact. |\n\n## Tenant Users & Login\n_Tenant-scoped via `X-API-Key`. A tenant can have several login profiles — one `admin` plus any number of `staff`._\n\n| Method | Path | Auth | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/login` | api key, public | `{ email, password }` → `{ token }` (role from the tenant user record) |\n| POST | `/admin/users` | api key + admin | Add another login profile to your own tenant. `role` must be `admin` or `staff` (defaults to `staff` if omitted) — any other value, including `superadmin`, returns `400 invalid role`. Omit `password` to auto-generate. |\n| GET | `/admin/users` | api key + admin | `?page&limit` |\n| PUT | `/admin/users/:id/status` | api key + admin | `{ status: active \\| suspended }` |\n\n## Public storefront routes\n_Tenant-scoped via `X-API-Key` only — no user login._\n\n| Method | Path | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/destinations` | `?category&region&season&page&limit` |\n| GET | `/destinations/:slug` | |\n| GET | `/blogs` | Published only. `?page&limit` |\n| GET | `/blogs/:slug` | |\n| POST | `/bookings` | Customer submits a tour booking |\n| GET | `/cars` | `?type&fuel&page&limit` |\n| GET | `/cars/:slug` | |\n| POST | `/rentals` | Customer requests a car rental |\n| POST | `/airport-transfers` | Customer requests a pickup/drop-off |\n| POST | `/contact` | Contact form submission |\n\n## Tenant admin routes\n_Requires both `X-API-Key` and a Bearer token with role `admin` scoped to that tenant, obtained from `POST /login`._\n\n| Method | Path | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| POST | `/admin/destinations` | Full model — unset fields default to zero value |\n| PUT | `/admin/destinations/:id` | Partial update (`$set`) |\n| DELETE | `/admin/destinations/:id` | |\n| POST | `/admin/blogs` | Created as `draft` regardless of body |\n| PUT | `/admin/blogs/:id` | Partial update |\n| POST | `/admin/blogs/:id/publish` | No body |\n| GET | `/admin/bookings` | `?page&limit` |\n| GET | `/admin/bookings/:id` | |\n| PUT | `/admin/bookings/:id/status` | `pending → confirmed → completed`, or `cancelled` |\n| POST | `/admin/cars` | |\n| PUT | `/admin/cars/:id` | Partial update |\n| DELETE | `/admin/cars/:id` | |\n| GET | `/admin/rentals` | `?page&limit` |\n| GET | `/admin/rentals/:id` | |\n| PUT | `/admin/rentals/:id/status` | `pending → confirmed → completed`, or `cancelled` |\n| GET | `/admin/airport-transfers` | `?page&limit` |\n| GET | `/admin/airport-transfers/:id` | |\n| PUT | `/admin/airport-transfers/:id/status` | `pending → confirmed → completed`, or `cancelled` |\n| GET | `/admin/contact-messages` | `?page&limit` |\n| PUT | `/admin/contact-messages/:id/status` | `new → read → responded` |\n\n---\nSourced from `internal/handler/router.go`. Re-check this doc if that file changes — nothing here is hand-maintained separately from the code.",
      "item": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Platform (Superadmin)",
      "description": "Manages tenants themselves. Not tenant-scoped — no X-API-Key needed. Login is public; every other request here requires a Bearer token whose role is \"superadmin\", obtained from Login below. The very first platform user is created automatically on server startup from the SUPERADMIN_EMAIL/SUPERADMIN_PASSWORD env vars (see .env.example) — log in with those to get your first {{superadmin_token}}, then use [Admin Users] to add more platform accounts if needed. Create Tenant returns the tenant's raw api_key exactly once — copy it into the {{tenant_api_key}} collection variable to run every other folder in this collection. If contact_email is set, it also bootstraps an \"admin\" login profile for that email and returns its one-time password under login.password — copy that (and the email) into {{tenant_admin_password}} / {{tenant_admin_email}} so the Auth folder's Login request works. The subscription requests below track a tenant's plan/billing status internally — there's no live payment provider wired in yet, so plan changes are applied directly through these endpoints.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/platform/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["platform", "login"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{superadmin_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{superadmin_password}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[Admin Users] Create Platform User",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{superadmin_token}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/platform/admins",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["platform", "admins"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Second Superadmin\",\n  \"email\": \"ops2@eandstravel.example.com\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[Admin Users] List Platform Users",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{superadmin_token}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/platform/admins?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["platform", "admins"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "[Admin Users] Update Platform User Status",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{superadmin_token}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/platform/admins/{{platform_user_id}}/status",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["platform", "admins", "{{platform_user_id}}", "status"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"suspended\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Tenant",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{superadmin_token}}", "type": "string" }]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/platform/tenants",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["platform", "tenants"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nomad Trails LLC\",\n  \"slug\": \"nomad-trails\",\n  \"contact_email\": \"ops@nomadtrails.example.com\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Tenants",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
